# Upload button located via label <p> sibling traversal — ported from legacy framework.
# Finds the <p> containing the label, navigates to parent div, then sibling div containing button.
# More reliable than ancestor-based scoping — works across all upload button structures on summary page.
# {label} replaced at runtime with the document type label text.
iNRCISYFUploadBtn                   = //p[contains(normalize-space(),'{label}')]/parent::div/following-sibling::div/descendant::button
